All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, WebSocketListener
public class NotificationService extends android.app.Service implements WebSocketListener
This class sets a service that runs a Websocket allowing the notification websocket listener to run on every page
